<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَيْدَهُ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> المُرَادُ:</span> سَحَرَتُهُ الَّذِينَ يَكِيدُ بِهِمْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا تَفْتَرُوا}</span> ... لَا تَخْتَلِقُوا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَيُسْحِتَكُمْ}</span> ... فَيَسْتَاصِلَكُمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِطَرِيقَتِكُمُ الْمُثْلَى}</span> ... طَرِيقَةِ السِّحْرِ العَظِيمَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَجْمِعُوا كَيْدَكُمْ}</span> ... فأَحْكِمُوا كَيْدَكُمْ، وَاعْزِمُوا عَلَيْهِ، وَلَا تَخْتَلِفُوا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَوْجَسَ}</span> ... فَشَعَرَ، وَأَحَسَّ فِي نَفْسِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَلْقَفْ}</span> ... تَبْتَلِعْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِّنْ خِلَافٍ}</span> ... مُخَالِفًا بِيْنَ الأَيْدِي وَالأَرْجُلِ، فَيَقْطَعُ يَدًا مِنْ جِهَةٍ، وَرِجْلًا مِنْ جِهَةٍ أُخْرَى.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُّؤْثِرَكَ}</span> ... نُفَضِّلَكَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَطَرَنَا}</span> ... خَلَقَنَا وَأَبْدَعَنَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
